# Namespace & Versioning Policy v1.0

## Schema: https://scope3.dev/voucher/2025-06/v1.0

### Version Strategy
- **Major versions** (v1.0, v2.0): Breaking changes requiring migration
- **Minor versions** (v1.1, v1.2): Backward-compatible additions
- **Patch versions** (v1.0.1): Documentation/annotation fixes only

### Deprecation Policy
1. **24-month notice** before deprecating any major version
2. **Parallel support** for 12 months after new major version release
3. **Migration tools** provided for all breaking changes
4. **Announcement channels**: https://scope3.dev/schemas/updates

### Namespace Evolution
- v1.0: Initial release (2025-06)
- v1.1: Planned Q4 2025 - ISSB alignment
- v2.0: Target 2027 - Post-CSRD implementation review

### Backward Compatibility Commitments
- No removal of mandatory elements within major version
- New optional elements via minor version increments
- Assertion additions allowed in minor versions
- Unit/currency expansions via external schema updates

### Governance Board
- Technical Lead: Schema Architecture Team
- Regulatory Advisor: ESG Compliance Unit
- External Reviewer: Big 4 Assurance Partner